text: Alycidae is a family of mites, or endeostigs, in the suborder Endeostigmata. There are at least 6 genera in Alycidae. ==Genera== These six genera belong to the family Alycidae: * Alycus C.L.Koch, 1842 * Amphialycus Zachvatkin, 1949 * Coccalicus Willmann, 1952 * Laminamichaelia Uusitalo, 2010 * Orthacarus Zachvatkin, 1949 * Petralycus Grandjean, 1943 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * Category:Acari
title: Alycidae
